El-Bashir also wishes that the Chinese people could realize
their wish for progress, development and stability while unifying
all their territories under the flag of one China.
</P>
<P>
In his message, South African President Nelson Mandela said the
historic first step of the resumption of China's exercise of
sovereignty over Hong Kong marks the end of a period of history,
heralds in a new era and is the manifestation of the policy of
"one country, two system" which the government and people of China
may carry into the new millennium. 
