<HEADLINE> Eritrea, Rwanda to Establish Joint Commission on </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
ADDIS ABABA, June 30 (Xinhua) -- Eritrea and Rwanda have
agreed to establish a permanent joint commission to promote
bilateral cooperation in the fields of human resources
development, commerce and trade, banking and investment, land and
water management, culture, defense and security.
</P>
