Jaime Gama and British Foreign Secretary Robin Cook respectively.
He will also meet with Japanese Foreign Minister Yukihiko Ikeda,
Australian Foreign Minister Alexander Downer, Russian Foreign
Minister Y.M. Primakov and German Foreign Minister Klaus Kinkel
this morning.  
