<HEADLINE> Albanian Prime Minister Hails Hong Kong's Return </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TIRANA, June 29 (Xinhua) -- Albanian Prime Minister Bashkim
Fino said here today that the return of Hong Kong to China is an
event of historical and international significance.
</P>
<P>
"China's resumption of the exercise of sovereignty over Hong
Kong is a result of the implementation of the concept of 'one
country, two systems' put forward by the late Chinese leader Deng
Xiaoping," Fino said in an exclusive interview with Xinhua.
</P>
<P>
"Hong Kong's return will help settle the Macao and Taiwan
issues and set an example for the settlement of the outstanding
issues in international relations," Fino said.
</P>
<P>
The successful development of China's economy has demonstrated
the talent, potential and creativity of the Chinese people and the
correctness of China's economic policies, he added. 
</P>
